    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 40-43.</p><p>Legendary Forms</p><p>Also at 20th level, you gain the ability to transform into greater forms as part of your wild shape. When you use your Wild Shape, you can expend 1 Legendary Point to turn into any elemental, fey, or monstrosity you have seen before of a Challenge Rating equal to or lower than 10. You transform into an average example of that creature, one without any class levels or the Spellcasting trait. You can’t use any legendary actions, legendary resistances, or lair actions of the new form.</p></div>",
